_sText:
this map took wayyy more time to make than i intended. 
it went from a 20s strafe map with a couple boosters to a 1 minute long portal adventure (my sleep schedule will never recover)
the first stage was designed by saturn,
map aesthetic inspired by a vmf called cityscape made by dream

lots of pretty planets (asset pack coming soon) and the vibe is spacey and ethereal as usual. 
there is a bonus by moonky, and showcase run by cxvewow (thank you)
i couldnt have completed this project without the endless support from guad and granis, 
also thank you to all of the playtesters and critics, i am so grateful for all of the help.
